description: The Fund aims to achieve a return on your investment, through a combination of capital growth and income, which reflects the return of the MSCI Europe High Dividend Yield ESG Reduced Carbon Target Select Index. On 1st June 2022, the benchmark changed from MSCI Europe High Dividend Yield 4% Issuer Capped Index to MSCI Europe High Dividend Yield ESG Reduced Carbon Target Select Index. The change will be reflected in the benchmark data.
name: iShares MSCI Europe Quality Dividend Advanced UCITS ETF
